This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) category as it deals with depth estimation from monocular images. The use of Edge-Guided post-processing and Atrous Spatial Pyramid Pooling (ASPP) also suggests that it may belong to the Robotics (cs.RO) category as these techniques are commonly used in robotics applications. Additionally, the use of self-supervised learning suggests that it may belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) category. The paper also involves the use of neural networks, which suggests that it may belong to the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) category. Finally, the mention of achieving real-time performance suggests that it may belong to the Multimedia (cs.MM) category.
